data.description:
*VA Assumable Loan at 2.65%!!!* This charming abode offers a practical floor plan that includes 3 cozy bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a dedicated flex/office space to accommodate your remote work, a play room, or anything else you may need.

As you enter, the living room greets you with a warm ambiance, highlighted by a wood-burning fireplace set against a brick backdrop, perfect for chilly evenings. The open layout ensures a seamless flow from the living area to the dining space, where natural light spills through the windows, creating an inviting atmosphere for family meals.

Cooking enthusiasts will appreciate the kitchen's ample cabinet space and practical design, complete with all the essentials and a center island for added prep space. The LVP flooring throughout the home marries durability with style, ensuring a low-maintenance living environment that doesn’t sacrifice aesthetic appeal.

Retreat to the privacy of the primary suite, boasting a spacious layout that includes a luxurious en-suite bathroom equipped with a large tub and separate shower, providing a spa-like experience every day.

Step outside to the generous backyard, where there’s plenty of room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply basking in the sun. The covered patio area serves as a serene spot for relaxation or entertaining guests.

This property is more than just a house; it's a canvas awaiting your personal touch to create memories that will last a lifetime. Come see how 2404 Basalt Dr can be the backdrop to the next chapter in your story.
